## Hadith Content Attribution

The hadith content in this application is sourced from:
- **Riyāḍ al-Ṣāliḥīn** (The Gardens of the Righteous) by Imam An-Nawawi
- Authentic Islamic scholarly translations
- Verified hadith collections from established Islamic sources

The hadith content is used for educational and spiritual purposes in accordance with Islamic principles of knowledge sharing. All hadith are properly attributed with source references and hadith numbers.